01:16.280 --> 01:22.560
It says, Dear Miss Ellinson, thank you for your query and interest in our representation.

01:22.560 --> 01:26.840
I've had a chance to review Awoken, and though what you're attempting is very ambitious,

01:26.920 --> 01:29.000
