There is that but there's also, if we did go with a traditional publisher we'd kind

08:01.680 --> 08:03.600
of have to give up our ruse.

08:03.600 --> 08:06.760
It would be harder, yeah, he would have to drop the Sarah Ellison.

08:06.760 --> 08:13.320
Yeah, we would still use the pseudonym but there wouldn't be the ruse, we wouldn't have

08:13.320 --> 08:17.320
our fake author getting in Facebook fights with reviewers that gave her a bad review,

08:17.320 --> 08:19.520
which she totally would by the way.

08:19.520 --> 08:20.520
She's that person.

