And also we kind of have a leg up that other potential self-publishing authors might not

08:36.240 --> 08:38.360
in that we have an audience.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.360
You!

08:39.360 --> 08:41.720
Viewers like you.

08:41.720 --> 08:45.080
We have an audience that has been following this for months so obviously they're like

08:45.080 --> 08:47.080
yeah we want it, we want it now, we want to see the horror.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.080
Or hope that you don't.

08:48.240 --> 08:51.400
Well, I mean, it is kind of a push-pull.

08:51.400 --> 08:59.900
There is a lot of benefit to traditional publishing still, but you have complete creative control

08:59.900 --> 09:04.360
over your own product and how you market it when you self-publish.

09:04.360 --> 09:06.080
